==未来扩展==
[[File:Bay_bridge_from_the_air.JPG|right]]

2004年12月，一项研究认为，预计2025年，大桥交通会增加40%。次年，马里兰州长罗伯特·埃利成立专案组，再次开会探讨建立新的跨海交通的可行性。<ref name="second bridge">{{cite news|last=Berman|first=Dori|url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4183/is_20050627/ai_n14693744|title=Task force says second Chesapeake Bay bridge is best option|publisher=The Baltimore Daily Record|date=June 27, 2005|accessdate=2008-02-05|archive-date=2016-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160108225236/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4183/is_20050627/ai_n14693744|dead-url=no}}</ref>  专案组认为，大桥仍为建立新路线的最佳方式，共探讨了四个地理位置：巴尔的摩县到肯特县，安妮阿伦德尔县到安妮女王县（现存大桥的位置），安妮阿伦德尔或卡尔弗特县到塔尔博特县，和卡尔弗特县到多尔切斯特县。<ref name="task force pdf">{{cite web|url=http://www.mdta.state.md.us/mdta/BayCrossing/BriefingBook/Taskforce_Briefing_Book_2-001.pdf|title=Meeting #2: Bridge, Traffic, and Highway Issues|publisher=Maryland Transportation Authority|accessdate=2008-02-05|format=pdf|archive-date=2007-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070124043621/http://www.mdta.state.md.us/mdta/BayCrossing/BriefingBook/Taskforce_Briefing_Book_2-001.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>2006年底，专案组发布研究报告，但未提出最终建议；专案组人员请求额外时间继续研究。<ref name="WTOP-report released">{{cite news|last=Wyatt|first=Kristen|url=http://www.wtopnews.com/?nid=25&sid=896776|title=Bay Bridge Report Released without Recommendation|publisher=WTOP news|date=August 29, 2006|accessdate=2008-02-05|archive-date=2013-01-05|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130105084049/http://www.wtopnews.com/?nid=25&sid=896776|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

